Shadowrun: Dragonfall - Director's Cut - independent release successful campaign Dragonfall, which first appeared as an extension to the Shadowrun Returns.
Director's Cut version includes several enhancements and new content : 5 new missions, alternate endings , new music , redone UI , configuration options team reworked the role system and more. 09/21/14 Added updated the game to version 2.04

what's new
Update v2.04:

Corrections :
- Removed non-functional options in the settings menu.
- Fixed multiple application complexity indexes when loading the game in the middle of a mission.
- Fixed the use of Mana Fist

Corrections in Dragonfall Campaign:
- Fixed possible after plugging the mission The Harfeld Manor Run.
- Fixed possible plugging if the player accepts a mission companion Glory, leading to the end of the game .

installation
Mount image , install the game , copy the contents of the folder CODEX in the game folder , block game access to the Internet .

